oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Women at Dorian home
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Group portrait of several unidentified women standing outside the Dorian family home while dressed in formal wear. Handwriting towards the bottom of the photograph identifies one woman as Nina Savage. Note: this negative was cut in half.
